Event.create!(title: "PITCH Group 1", description: "at Stage 6. 105 of the most promising startups will battle it out in the group rounds of the competition. In this round, 10 of them will fight for a chance to move onto the semi-final. Competing startups will have three minutes to pitch, followed by a three-minute Q&A with our judging panel. With Anas CHANAA (CEO @ Nucleon Security), Alex Santos (CEO @ Barifix), Yaroslav Krempovych (General Manager @ Checkbox), Alexandre Ferreira (CTO @ outGoing), Ksenia Belkina (CEO @ Cardiomo) and Moaad El Aboudi (CEO @ Insight Solutions SA)", start_time: "2024-11-12 10:00:00", end_time: "2024-11-12 11:00:00")
Event.create!(title: "PITCH Group 2", description: "at Stage 9. 105 of the most promising startups will battle it out in the group rounds of the competition. In this round, 10 of them will fight for a chance to move onto the semi-final. Competing startups will have three minutes to pitch, followed by a three-minute Q&A with our judging panel. With Albert Brenner (Managing Director & Co-Founder @ OVRLAY), Esra Akdere (Co-Founder @ Time Travel VR Tour), Andreia Trigo (CEO @ Enhanced Fertility), Ryan Schmaltz (CEO @ Patient Ready, Inc.), Ksenia Belkina (CEO @ Cardiomo) and Anna Franziska Michel (CEO & Founder @ yoona.ai)", start_time: "2024-11-12 10:00:00", end_time: "2024-11-12 11:00:00")
Event.create!(title: "PITCH Group 3", description: "at Stand 12. 105 of the most promising startups will battle it out in the group rounds of the competition. In this round, 10 of them will fight for a chance to move onto the semi-final. Competing startups will have three minutes to pitch, followed by a three-minute Q&A with our judging panel. With Federico Leuze (AI Developer @ Resonisk), Mila (Ludmila) Aleshina (Co-founder @ incorpo studio), Emmanuel Evarist-Chika (CEO & Co-founder @ LINK), Heather Mitche (Chief of staff @ Innerworks), Jeff Hu (CEO & Founder @ Turing Space) and Brittany Kaiser (Founder @ Own Your Data)", start_time: "2024-11-12 10:00:00", end_time: "2024-11-12 11:00:00")
Event.create!(title: "Meet the Adobe Experts", description: "at Stand E111. Meet with our experts to explore ways you can accelerate creative productivity with the power of generative AI within your team and organization. See a live demo or schedule a meeting with us!", start_time: "2024-11-12 10:00:00", end_time: "2024-11-12 12:30:00")
Event.create!(title: "Express Yourself with Adobe Express", description: "at Stand E111. Join us at the Adobe Express activation! Unleash your creativity by personalizing your own coffee mug. The perfect way to express yourself and create a unique piece with Adobe Express. The quick and easy create-anything app.", start_time: "2024-11-12 10:00:00", end_time: "2024-11-12 11:00:00")
Event.create!(title: "How to prepare for the age of AI in software", description: "at Roundtable. Kirill Skrygan, CEO of JetBrains, leads a discussion on how AI is transforming software development, from workflow changes to new skills. Explore the challenges and opportunities AI brings to building modern software products. With Kirill Skrygan (CEO @ JetBrains)", start_time: "2024-11-12 10:00:00", end_time: "2024-11-12 11:00:00")
Event.create!(title: "Making sense of the US elections", description: "at Roundtables. The results of American elections will have a profound (though not necessarily straightforward) impact on technology in the US and beyond. Join us to talk about how the November 2024 U.S. election might reshape the technological landscape in the years to come.", start_time: "2024-11-12 10:00:00", end_time: "2024-11-12 11:00:00")
Event.create!(title: "Navigating the EU AI act", description: "at Stage 15. The EU's new AI Act ushers in a transformative era of regulation for artificial intelligence. While the Act aims to ensure responsible development and use of AI, it also presents significant compliance challenges for companies. This panel delves deep into the Act's key provisions and explores the potential difficulties businesses might face during implementation. With Shelley McKinley (Chief Legal Officer @ Github), Adriano Koshiyama (Co-CEO & Co-Founder @ Holistic AI), Tasos Stampelos (Head of EU Public Policy @ Mozilla) and Ryan Browne (Correspondent @ CNBC)", start_time: "2024-11-12 10:10:00", end_time: "2024-11-12 10:35:00")
